snippet: Webb Simpson shot a six-under-par 64 to take a one-stroke lead over Henrik Stenson in Akron, Ohio. Simpson, the 2012 United States Open winner, had six birdies in eight holes.
abstract: Webb Simpson takes a one-stroke lead at Bridgestone International in Akron, Ohio.
lead_paragraph: Webb Simpson shot a six-under-par 64 to take a one-stroke lead over Henrik Stenson in Akron, Ohio. Simpson, the 2012 United States Open winner, had six birdies in eight holes.

headline.main: Simpson Leads at the Bridgestone Invitational
